message.body: Hi Nevynervine. I'm Donna, from just south of Philly. How are you?
Hello I'm Nevy I'm from California. I am well thank you!
Workin.. That's it... California? Wow! How did you hear about this study?
Craigslist. I've just been trying to find a job, and thought this would be a good time filler!
I saw it on CL too... Cool. What kind of work are you looking for?
Anything really. I've been working for theme parks since I was 15.
That's neat. I'm a copy editor.. I proofread and edit direct mail and email for non profits and banks
It's 11:18 here.. I have to be at work at 9 am and have an hour commute.. So I'm going to head to bed. I hope we can chat more
Oh gosh alright! Hopefully we do before the 23 hours is up!
